'''圣母大学爱尔兰战士队'''（{{lang-en|Notre Dame Fighting Irish}}）代表[[圣母大学|圣母大学]]参加[[国家大学体育协会|国家大学体育协会]]（{{lang|en|NCAA}}）第一级别的23项校际体育赛事，其中在许多项目中属于[[大西洋沿岸联盟|大西洋沿岸联盟]]。<ref name="nd_ACC_join_date">{{cite web|last=McMurphy|first=Brett|title=Big East, Notre Dame agree on exit|url=http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/9042949/notre-dame-big-east-agree-irish-exit-2-years-early-join-acc|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=March 12, 2013|archive-date=2013-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130312211826/http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/9042949/notre-dame-big-east-agree-irish-exit-2-years-early-join-acc|dead-url=no}}</ref>圣母大学也是全美同时参加NCAA最高级别的男子[[美式足球|美式足球]]与男子[[冰球|冰球]]比赛的15所学校之一。学校的代表色为金色与蓝色<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.und.com/trads/nd-m-fb-goldandblue.html | publisher=University of Notre Dame | title=Gold and Blue | accessdate=March 28, 2015 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214133922/http://www.und.com/trads/nd-m-fb-goldandblue.html | archive-date=2014-12-14 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，吉祥物为[[拉布列康|拉布列康]]。

